trans-unit.source: Currently, there is no complete way to retrieve the script, interval or ttl metadata for a registered check. Without this metadata it is not possible to tell if the data supplied with ansible represents a change to a check. As a result this does not attempt to determine changes and will always report a changed occurred. An API method is planned to supply this metadata so at that stage change management will be added.
